jwiki.core

Class Reply

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.json.JSONObject
      • jwiki.core.Reply

  • public class Reply
extends JSONObject
    Represents a reply from the server. A reply from a MediaWiki server is a JSONObject; this class is an extension to JSONObject, and contains some pre-processing and error detecting methods.
    Author:
    Fastily
